text: Jakob Olsson (born March 7, 1997) is a Swedish ice hockey player. He is currently playing with Frölunda HC of the Swedish Hockey League (SHL). Olsson made his Swedish Hockey League debut playing with Frölunda HC during the 2014–15 SHL season. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Frölunda HC players Category:Swedish ice hockey left wingers
